data.description: SHORT SALE. Enter into a world of modern charm & elegance with this adorable home in McClellan Ranch! Be welcomed by the large open floor plan showcasing wood-look tile flooring & sliding glass doors to the back patio. The fabulous kitchen displays recessed & pendant lighting, a walk-in pantry, cabinets & cupboards adorned with crown moulding, stainless steel appliances, granite counters, subway tile backsplash, & an island with a breakfast bar great for a quick meal. All bedrooms have plush carpets. Discover the primary bedroom, highlighting an elegant ensuite with dual sinks, garden tub, glass-enclosed rain shower, & a walk-in closet. The spacious backyard with its covered patio is ideal for weekend barbecues or simply enjoying a quiet moment. Don't miss out on this unique find!
